videos.description: Steve Kerr doesn't think the Warriors were in good enough shape in their opener and addresses how the team was impacted not having Draymond Green on the court.

videos.description: James Harden breaks down the Rockets' resilience, not having Chris Paul at full strength and still finding a way to defeat the Warriors.
